name: 1988 Turn Back the Clock Mad Dog Jones - thr33smas Insert - #3MAS11
description:
The Eleventh Day of thr33smas

Eleventh card in a series of 12 cards looking back at the highlights of the first 7 months of thr33som3s mints.

In Series 7, the Grotto saw the first instance of a player being traded from one team to another.  Mad Dog Jones was sent from the NFTs to the Cat Moms for a player to be named later.

MDJ promptly appeared in his first Cat Moms card and became the first thr33som3s subject to appear in two base series.  This thr33smas card is a painting of the original Series 7 painting.

The 12 Days of thr33smas is a chase 3v3nt. Collect all 12, #3MAS1 through #3MAS12, in the announced timeframe to receive #3MAS13 via airdrop.

This card is an INSERT. It has all established Standard Insert Utility and may compound additional Utilities over time. It is a thr33smas Insert and a Holiday Insert.  It was minted a few days after the 12 days of thr33smas 3v3nt, as thr33som3s was busy preparing for the first ever thr33zi3s drop ***** digital capture of original painting, gouache on vintage baseball card, 2021. ************ NFT image is for personal use, no commercial rights are granted. Twitter @thr33som3s and IG @thr33somes to see upcoming cards and new series. ************ ALL thr33som3s have FUTURE UTILITY.
